data.description: Walk into an open floor plan with plenty of natural light. Entertain guests in your spacious living/dining combo, boasting high ceilings and sits adjacent to the kitchen. The primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet and bathroom with walk in shower. There is also a guest suite downstairs with a full bathroom. Upstairs you will find a huge loft that overlooks the backyard and 2 additional bedrooms with a shared full bathroom. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in your private backyard oasis. This home has the biggest lot in the neighborhood. It also features a screened patio thats ideal for outdoor dining and relaxation, and the spacious backyard is perfect for gardening or family gatherings.  Roof is only 7 years old and brand new HVAC only 2 years old. HOA only $245 annually. (Professional photos will be uploaded Monday)
